## 6. Jell

OKR-focused check-in tool.

### Features

- Daily, weekly, and custom check-ins
- OKR/goal tracking tied to check-ins so updates are framed against goals
- Slack and Teams integration
- Reporting on goal progress over time

### Pros

- Strongest tool for tying daily updates to long-term goals
- Useful for orgs that already run OKRs
- Lighter weight than Steady's full goals feature

### Cons

- Cultural fit issue: teams that don't run OKRs find it forces structure they don't want
- Less sophisticated mood/wellbeing layer than Range or DailyBot
- Limited integration depth compared to Steady
- No AI features, no AI agent tracking

