## 7. Slack Workflow Builder (the free baseline)

Slack's native automation tool.

### Features

- Build a custom standup workflow that DMs members on a schedule with form-style questions
- Posts responses to a channel
- Free, native, no third-party app needed

### Pros

- Free, no extra account or vendor risk
- Data stays in Slack; nothing to onboard the team to
- Good enough for very small teams that just want async question answers

### Cons

- No analytics, no rollups, no integrations beyond Slack itself
- No mood tracking, no blocker escalation, no goals
- Manual setup per workflow; not optimized for standups
- No AI features at all

